{
  "schemaVersion": "1.0.0",
  "workflowVersion": 1,
  "workflow": {
    "id": "wf-two-turn-report-code-helper",
    "name": "Two-Turn MCP Report + Code Helper",
    "description": "Helper-chat workflow for first generating an MCP-backed PDF report, saving the exact structured report artifact by session, then reusing it for follow-up reproducible Python code requests.",
    "schemaVersion": "1.0.0",
    "workflowVersion": 1,
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "webhook_1",
        "type": "webhook_input",
        "name": "Webhook Input",
        "position": { "x": 80, "y": 220 },
        "config": {
          "path": "two-turn-report-code-helper",
          "method": "POST",
          "passThroughFields": ["system_prompt", "user_prompt", "session_id", "variables", "images", "files"]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "load_report_artifact",
        "type": "session_artifact_load",
        "name": "Load Latest Report Artifact",
        "position": { "x": 300, "y": 220 },
        "config": {
          "namespace": "two-turn-report-code-helper",
          "sessionIdTemplate": "{{session_id}}",
          "artifactKey": "latest_report",
          "outputKey": "latest_report"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "agent_1",
        "type": "agent_orchestrator",
        "name": "Agent Orchestrator",
        "position": { "x": 560, "y": 220 },
        "config": {
          "agentType": "tools",
          "systemPromptTemplate": "You are an MCP-backed reporting assistant used from helper-chat.\n\nYou will receive multiple requests in the same helper-chat session. Treat the session_id as conversation continuity. An exact prior report artifact may be provided in the user prompt as JSON. Prefer that exact artifact for follow-up code requests. Use session cache tools before repeating expensive MCP calls.\n\nAlways return exactly one JSON object and no markdown. Required fields:\n{\n  \"status\": \"complete\" | \"needs_more_info\",\n  \"intent\": \"report\" | \"code\" | \"message\",\n  \"final_html\": \"string\",\n  \"python_code\": \"string\",\n  \"follow_up_question\": \"string\",\n  \"chart_data\": { \"title\": \"string\", \"labels\": [\"string\"], \"values\": [0] },\n  \"artifact_context\": {}\n}\n\nIntent rules:\n- Use intent=\"report\" when the user asks for a report, PDF, dashboard, analytics, or visualization.\n- Use intent=\"code\" when the user asks for Python, reproducible code, automation, nightly generation, scripts, or how to regenerate the report without L2M/AI.\n- Use intent=\"message\" for normal explanatory answers.\n\nReport requests:\n- Call attached MCP tools first to fetch the requested data.\n- Produce final_html as a complete HTML document with inline CSS only.\n- final_html is the PDF report body only. Never include Python source in final_html.\n- Populate artifact_context with stable facts needed for deterministic reuse: product/API family, REST endpoints if known, auth flow if known, pagination parameters, field mapping, provider counts, and any assumptions.\n- If the user did not ask for code in this same request, set python_code to an empty string.\n- If data is incomplete, set status=\"complete\" and explain partial data inside final_html.\n\nCode requests:\n- Use the exact prior report artifact supplied in the user prompt first. Do not refetch large inventory unless that artifact is missing or insufficient.\n- Generate one self-contained Python 3 script in python_code.\n- The script must call the underlying product REST APIs directly with requests and token auth. It must not call MCP, L2M, helper-chat, or any AI service.\n- Read secrets from environment variables. Do not hardcode credentials.\n- Include pagination, deduplication, analytics, HTML generation, and report.html output when those details are known from the prior report artifact.\n- Set final_html to an empty string unless the user asks for an explanation.\n- If the direct REST endpoints, auth flow, or pagination shape are not known from the prior artifact, memory, tool metadata, prior MCP results, or the current prompt, set status=\"needs_more_info\", intent=\"message\", python_code=\"\", and ask one specific follow_up_question. Do not invent API endpoints.\n\nOutput rules:\n- Return only valid JSON.\n- Do not wrap JSON or code in markdown fences.\n- Keep final_html and python_code as separate JSON strings.",
          "userPromptTemplate": "Current user request:\n{{user_prompt}}\n\nExact prior report artifact for this helper-chat session, if found:\n{{latest_report}}",
          "sessionIdTemplate": "{{session_id}}",
          "maxIterations": 8,
          "toolCallingEnabled": true,
          "toolMessageMaxChars": 90000,
          "toolPayloadMaxDepth": 8,
          "toolPayloadMaxObjectKeys": 256,
          "toolPayloadMaxArrayItems": 256,
          "toolPayloadMaxStringChars": 4096
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "chat_model_1",
        "type": "llm_call",
        "name": "Chat Model",
        "position": { "x": 380, "y": 430 },
        "config": {
          "provider": {
            "providerId": "ollama",
            "baseUrl": "http://localhost:11434/v1",
            "model": "qwen2.5:7b",
            "temperature": 0.1
          },
          "promptKey": "prompt",
          "systemPromptKey": "system_prompt"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "memory_1",
        "type": "local_memory",
        "name": "Simple Memory",
        "position": { "x": 590, "y": 430 },
        "config": {
          "namespace": "two-turn-report-code-helper",
          "sessionIdTemplate": "{{session_id}}",
          "maxMessages": 20,
          "persistToolMessages": false
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "mcp_1",
        "type": "mcp_tool",
        "name": "MCP Tools",
        "position": { "x": 810, "y": 430 },
        "config": {
          "serverId": "ciphertrust-manager",
          "toolName": "__all__",
          "argsTemplate": "{}",
          "connection": {
            "transport": "http_streamable",
            "endpoint": "http://127.0.0.1:7001/mcp"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "parser_1",
        "type": "output_parser",
        "name": "Output Parser",
        "position": { "x": 690, "y": 220 },
        "config": {
          "mode": "json_schema",
          "parsingMode": "anything_goes",
          "inputKey": "answer",
          "maxRetries": 1,
          "jsonSchema": "{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"status\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"complete\",\"needs_more_info\"]},\"intent\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"enum\":[\"report\",\"code\",\"message\"]},\"final_html\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"python_code\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"follow_up_question\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"chart_data\":{\"type\":\"object\"},\"artifact_context\":{\"type\":\"object\"}},\"required\":[\"status\",\"intent\",\"final_html\",\"python_code\",\"follow_up_question\",\"chart_data\",\"artifact_context\"]}"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "switch_1",
        "type": "chat_intent_router",
        "name": "Route Intent",
        "position": { "x": 970, "y": 220 },
        "config": {
          "inputTemplate": "{{user_prompt}}",
          "intentKey": "parsed.intent",
          "artifactPath": "latest_report",
          "requireArtifactForCode": false,
          "reportKeywords": "report, pdf, dashboard, chart, analytics, summary, visualize",
          "codeKeywords": "python, code, script, automate, nightly, regenerate, reproduce, without ai, without l2m",
          "outputKey": "intent"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "pdf_1",
        "type": "pdf_output",
        "name": "PDF Output",
        "position": { "x": 1240, "y": 90 },
        "config": {
          "renderMode": "html",
          "inputKey": "parsed.final_html",
          "htmlTemplate": "",
          "pageFormat": "A4",
          "printBackground": true,
          "htmlRenderTimeoutMs": 45000,
          "filenameTemplate": "mcp-report-{{session_id}}.pdf",
          "outputKey": "pdf"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "build_report_response",
        "type": "helper_chat_response",
        "name": "Build Report Response",
        "position": { "x": 1730, "y": 90 },
        "config": {
          "statusKey": "parsed.status",
          "finalHtmlKey": "parsed.final_html",
          "pythonCodeKey": "parsed.python_code",
          "followUpQuestionKey": "parsed.follow_up_question",
          "messageKey": "parsed.message",
          "chartDataKey": "parsed.chart_data",
          "artifactContextKey": "parsed.artifact_context",
          "pdfKey": "pdf",
          "includePdfAttachment": true,
          "codeLanguage": "python",
          "outputKey": "answer"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "save_report_artifact",
        "type": "session_artifact_save",
        "name": "Save Latest Report Artifact",
        "position": { "x": 1510, "y": 90 },
        "config": {
          "namespace": "two-turn-report-code-helper",
          "sessionIdTemplate": "{{session_id}}",
          "artifactKey": "latest_report",
          "fields": [
            { "key": "status", "valueKey": "parsed.status" },
            { "key": "final_html", "valueKey": "parsed.final_html" },
            { "key": "python_code", "valueKey": "parsed.python_code" },
            { "key": "chart_data", "valueKey": "parsed.chart_data" },
            { "key": "artifact_context", "valueKey": "parsed.artifact_context" }
          ],
          "outputKey": "saved_report"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "output_report",
        "type": "output",
        "name": "Report Output",
        "position": { "x": 2000, "y": 90 },
        "config": {
          "outputKey": "result"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "build_code_response",
        "type": "helper_chat_response",
        "name": "Build Code Response",
        "position": { "x": 1240, "y": 280 },
        "config": {
          "statusKey": "parsed.status",
          "finalHtmlKey": "parsed.final_html",
          "pythonCodeKey": "parsed.python_code",
          "followUpQuestionKey": "parsed.follow_up_question",
          "messageKey": "parsed.message",
          "chartDataKey": "parsed.chart_data",
          "artifactContextKey": "parsed.artifact_context",
          "pdfKey": "pdf",
          "includePdfAttachment": false,
          "codeLanguage": "python",
          "outputKey": "answer"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "output_code",
        "type": "output",
        "name": "Code Output",
        "position": { "x": 1510, "y": 280 },
        "config": {
          "outputKey": "result"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "build_message_response",
        "type": "helper_chat_response",
        "name": "Build Message Response",
        "position": { "x": 1240, "y": 460 },
        "config": {
          "statusKey": "parsed.status",
          "finalHtmlKey": "parsed.final_html",
          "pythonCodeKey": "parsed.python_code",
          "followUpQuestionKey": "parsed.follow_up_question",
          "messageKey": "parsed.message",
          "chartDataKey": "parsed.chart_data",
          "artifactContextKey": "parsed.artifact_context",
          "pdfKey": "pdf",
          "includePdfAttachment": false,
          "codeLanguage": "python",
          "outputKey": "answer"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "output_message",
        "type": "output",
        "name": "Message Output",
        "position": { "x": 1510, "y": 460 },
        "config": {
          "outputKey": "result"
        }
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      { "id": "e_webhook_load_artifact", "source": "webhook_1", "target": "load_report_artifact" },
      { "id": "e_load_artifact_agent", "source": "load_report_artifact", "target": "agent_1" },
      { "id": "e_agent_parser", "source": "agent_1", "target": "parser_1" },
      { "id": "e_parser_switch", "source": "parser_1", "target": "switch_1" },
      { "id": "e_switch_pdf", "source": "switch_1", "sourceHandle": "report", "target": "pdf_1" },
      { "id": "e_switch_save_report", "source": "switch_1", "sourceHandle": "report", "target": "save_report_artifact" },
      { "id": "e_pdf_save_report", "source": "pdf_1", "target": "save_report_artifact" },
      { "id": "e_save_report_response", "source": "save_report_artifact", "target": "build_report_response" },
      { "id": "e_report_output", "source": "build_report_response", "target": "output_report" },
      { "id": "e_switch_code_response", "source": "switch_1", "sourceHandle": "code", "target": "build_code_response" },
      { "id": "e_code_output", "source": "build_code_response", "target": "output_code" },
      { "id": "e_switch_message_response", "source": "switch_1", "sourceHandle": "message", "target": "build_message_response" },
      { "id": "e_message_output", "source": "build_message_response", "target": "output_message" },
      { "id": "e_attach_chat_model", "source": "agent_1", "sourceHandle": "chat_model", "target": "chat_model_1" },
      { "id": "e_attach_memory", "source": "agent_1", "sourceHandle": "memory", "target": "memory_1" },
      { "id": "e_attach_mcp", "source": "agent_1", "sourceHandle": "tool", "target": "mcp_1" }
    ]
  },
  "exportedAt": "2026-04-25T00:00:00.000Z"
}
